close_reason: "Shipped TypeScript-only extension loading (ADR pm-m1uz). engines>=22.18 + @types/node ^22; all first-party packages, docs/examples, and the scaffolder point manifest entry at ./index.ts; committed compiled .js removed; runtime-loaders + gen-package-runtime-loaders.mjs resolve runtime.ts (JS loader variant dropped); CI/nightly/auto-release/docs workflows + esbuild bundler target Node 22/24 (Node 20 dropped); tsconfig.examples.json + allowImportingTsExtensions added; scaffolder next_steps fixed (no npm run build) and all README/docstring drift reframed; 8 spec files reconciled (runtime.js->runtime.ts, manifest entry, scaffold scripts, src-not-dist mocks) and the dogfood harness type-checks the scaffold then loads .ts directly."
